{"tid":1001433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本昆蟲狂熱少年的奇異初戀　與蟑螂相戀1年：曾幻想與牠做愛","createTime":"2019-01-30T06:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T11:12:19.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"6f70924e85b6d9067213d7102c05e21715b18867","tid":1001433,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"日本有一名從小愛昆蟲的男生，不但研究昆蟲飲食，更與蟑螂相戀，視之為性幻想對象。據《Asian Boss》報道，篠原祐太從小就十分熱愛昆蟲，甚至會偷偷進食，但一直都不敢向別人說，怕會被人欺凌。直至後來聯合國發表吃昆蟲的益處後，他才勇敢地說出自己愛吃蟲的事實。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2260000/2262510/2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2260000%2F2262510%2F2_600.jpg&h=21a1de91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲ 篠原祐太與Lisa相戀1年。(圖片來源：Asian Boss影片截圖)<br />\n<br />\n現年24歲篠原祐太因為聯合國糧食及農業組織發表一份報告，提到吃昆蟲的益處，才勇敢地說出自己愛吃蟲。除了愛吃蟲外，熱愛大自然的他，家中亦養了不同動物、昆蟲，例如蛇、蟋蟀、蟑螂等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2260000/2262510/DvwSzdSUUAAldJO_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2260000%2F2262510%2FDvwSzdSUUAAldJO_600.jpg&h=800047bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲ 篠原祐太熱愛大自然。(圖片來源：篠原祐太Twitter)<br />\n<br />\n當中他就在昆蟲中找到初戀Lisa。Lisa是一隻非洲蟑螂，養殖期間他被Lisa深深吸引，覺得自己可與Lisa溝通，甚至在Lisa在生時，曾幻想跟牠做愛。<br />\n<br />\n    我對牠是100%認真的，沒有任何女生可比Lisa更吸引。我曾幻想與牠做愛很多次。我知道這是不可能的，<span style=\"color: red;\">但我會想像Lisa是隻超大型的蟑螂或我縮小了地做愛。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2260000/2262510/1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2260000%2F2262510%2F1_600.jpg&h=563f0c61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲ 篠原祐太指自己對Lisa 100%認真。(圖片來源：Asian Boss影片截圖)<br />\n<br />\n不過由於非洲蟑螂的壽命短暫，所以相戀1年後，Lisa便死去了。Lisa離世後，他決定虔誠地吃掉Lisa：<br />\n<br />\n    如今，Lisa會永遠在我心中，可以永遠地活在我的身體裏。<br />\n<br />\n篠原祐太一直致力推廣昆蟲食物，曾與東京一間拉麵店合作，推出「昆蟲拉麵」，4小時內就售罄了限量100碗，又研究了昆蟲甜品、雞尾酒都大受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2262510/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%98%86%E8%9F%B2%E7%8B%82%E7%86%B1%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%87%E7%95%B0%E5%88%9D%E6%88%80%E3%80%80%E8%88%87%E8%9F%91%E8%9E%82%E7%9B%B8%E6%88%801%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%9A%E6%9B%BE%E5%B9%BB%E6%83%B3%E8%88%87%E7%89%A0%E5%81%9A%E6%84%9B?mtc=10019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2262510%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%2598%2586%25E8%259F%25B2%25E7%258B%2582%25E7%2586%25B1%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A5%2587%25E7%2595%25B0%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%2588%2580%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%259F%2591%25E8%259E%2582%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2588%25801%25E5%25B9%25B4%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25B9%25BB%25E6%2583%25B3%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%2589%25A0%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%2584%259B%3Fmtc%3D10019&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=b99db5c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2262510/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%98%86%E8%9F%B2%E7%8B%82%E7%86%B1%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%87%E7%95%B0%E5%88%9D%E6%88%80%E3%80%80%E8%88%87%E8%9F%91%E8%9E%82%E7%9B%B8%E6%88%801%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%9A%E6%9B%BE%E5%B9%BB%E6%83%B3%E8%88%87%E7%89%A0%E5%81%9A%E6%84%9B?mtc=10019</a>"},{"pid":"6e9ec76ebb168a909f60d2a68fbbd51dc662f9a5","tid":1001433,"uid":5649,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T07:02:18.000Z","msg":"變態就認啦<br />\n又想食又想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8765dfc553cd9014897666d780dfe9fa59c7e1c","tid":1001433,"uid":199636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T07:02:47.000Z","msg":"Jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a425a2ec163719f0e3c68c09fcc6c7e286af653f","tid":1001433,"uid":140009,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T07:04:35.000Z","msg":"我操"},{"pid":"5616a6aad6a63681b4806236c88126cd607bfe81","ti